text: Maritza Corredor Alvarez (born 21 January 1969) is a road cyclist from Colombia. She represented her nation at the 1996 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports- reference.com Category:Colombian female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Colombia Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:1969 births
